RELEASE POLICY
Version number is major.minor.patch
Major number will be increased if/when a strong redesign of the library will be necessary.
Minor number is increased when new features are added.
Patch number is increased with bug fixes.
For a given major.minor branch, the latest release (i.e. highest patch number) is the most reliable.

DOWNLOADS.
- iotk1.0.1.tar.gz

